Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please just wait, Shinichi. You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not at all wrong about this, Sumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have the gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!\NNot even a trace of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait!\NPlease don't abandon our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were an ordinary household,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,one without supernatural abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I likely would have been able\Nto love Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry, Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't have much time,\Nso I'm afraid this is all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I won't be able to protect you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My girl, I know that you'll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Soon you'll see,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}everything will be different\Nfor you one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream of mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,MY HAPPY MARRIAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 4\NTHE GIFT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yurie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Miss Miyo? What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping\Nthat I could ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo gave me something so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to get him\Na nice gift as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, the dishes aren't done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The dishes can wait,\Nit's not like they're going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's more important is to decide\Nwhat to gift the Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My budget for this\Nisn't impressive though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that I could buy\Nanything lavish. Nothing to his equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to buy anything expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Making something for him is an option too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Make it for him?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How about making him something\Nthat he would see or use on a daily basis?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're the one making it for him,\NMiss Miyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no doubt\Nhe would be happy with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure... he feels that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wonder what I could make for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}AN INTRODUCTORY GUIDE TO HANDICRAFT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That braided cord is pretty,\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I've found the one.\NThis is what I'll make.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Lord Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you... be okay with me\Nleaving the house for a little bit today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, there's an errand I need to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Miss Yurie's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wait,\NI can go with you on another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... it's all right. I can take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then be careful out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go following any strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,take this with you whenever you go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you for the kind gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:05:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure it's always with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very important\Nthat you heed my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care, Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An amulet!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never seen anything...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...like this before.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How sweet of him!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaya has just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you greet her\Nwith that frown on your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,your fiancée's gonna get all upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya Saimori is a lot, isn't she?\NHow's that going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't something I chose to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as noble as they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji, the diligent and obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All of my suffering is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always off playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first-born son,\Nso stop wandering off and act--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You never cease to amaze.\NBeing nice and not nice all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just saying it was enough, you jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They have quite the variety,\Ndon't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are\Nso many options to choose from,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but what would suit him?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming in today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the colors you picked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you found what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too. Just lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to start braiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, before we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot, we ran out of salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to go and get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.\NThose sorts of tasks are part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be quick. Please wait here\Nfor just a moment, Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well.\NIs that my sister I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I guess it has been a while,\Nmy sweet darling Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Mr. Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The warm welcome is greatly appreciated,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,despite my short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for visiting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored that you would take the time\Nto come and see me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,despite how busy you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us, what matter could bring someone\Nsuch as yourself here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- I have some things to discuss.\N- Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo? Why? Has she done something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping\Nwe could make our engagement official,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,as I intend to marry her\Nin the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Having said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the need to establish\Nour relationship from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,By that,\NI mean the one between our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you...\NWhat do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,marriages for those of us\Nin positions of power are "moves".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They are usually established\Non mutual interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,On my end, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have reservations in regards to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,providing any form of reciprocation\Nin this marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We know\Nthe kinds of things you did to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The hell you forced Miyo to live through.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a treat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seeing my dear sister alive\Nis actually kind of a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're walking around in public
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,wearing that shabby kimono\Nyou always wore,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that means Mr. Kudo abandoned you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A sad sack of potatoes you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It... it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't help if it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no way that my mediocre sister
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}could ever end up\Nwith someone so accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was truly inevitable,\Nyou being kicked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great that you walked out of it\Nalive though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We should head out. Kaya, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}- Why don't-- Argh!\N- Stand still and be quiet, Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}After everything you've dealt with\Nin your sad little life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I think you'd probably wanna die,\Nwouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's almost painful to imagine\Nsuch a dreadful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Providing you with her dowry is no issue
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You will give her an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sincerely and face-to-face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't force you\Nif you would prefer not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you don't,\Nwe cut ties here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do let me know if you're ever\Nin need of money, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you crawled around on the ground\Nand begged desperately for a few coins,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I could consider giving you some.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hmph. Nothing to say as usual.\NJust like the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No matter where you go,\Nyou're always the same, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I... I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}- I'm so sorry.\N- Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry that took me so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And who might these people be?\NFriends of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do?\NI'm Kaya, the youngest of the Saimoris.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much\Nfor watching over my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So I take it\Nthat you're a colleague of hers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,or you work together?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a ridiculous thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I am nowhere\Nnear the station of young Miss Miyo's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Colleagues? She will become
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the Lord Commander Kiyoka Kudo's wife,\Nand therefore a Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wife? Did you just say "wife"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes. You may call me Yurie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I apologize for the late introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I work as Miss Miyo's servant\Nin her household.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What a kind-hearted man your Lord is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He sounds like a giving soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I had assumed she was left out\Nin the street or abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose trusting the rumor mill\Nis never a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well then, we have other matters\Nthat need our attention for today,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}so if you would please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}All finished. Why don't we head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will need some time\Nto think about this apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait. But I will not wait for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I go and fix us a pot of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need any. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate you spending your time\Nin the city with me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:12:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Miss Yurie.\NIf you like, please rest as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm awful.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do I have to be this way?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hate myself.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he ever be satisfied\Nwith taking in a lowlife
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,like my sister as his wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kudo is likely just insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We had a guest today?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's so... beautiful!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're glad that you've returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't worry yourself over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The way Miss Miyo acted\Nin front of her sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked so terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was almost as if she was in pain\Nbeing near her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When we came home, it was like\Nthe emotions were drained out of her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have left her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me. May I speak with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to let you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The worries you have,\Nthe ones you keep to yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually, they'll fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, please allow yourself some peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever want to open up\Nabout what concerns you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I do?\NConfidence isn't something I can give.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You aren't entirely right,\NYoung Master.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is a way.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A woman can gain confidence\Nwhen she is shown love.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Love?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no need\Nto overcomplicate what I said.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All it takes is communicating\Nthat you cherish her in a meaningful way.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From there,\Nthe rest of it is up to Miss Miyo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Use sincerity and always engage her\Nwith your whole heart.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm positive\Nthat your feelings will reach her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's finished.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've made him a gift,\Nbut I don't know how to give it to him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I could do that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,May I come in for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a guest\Nwho has just arrived to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The years have flown by, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad to see you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It is truly wonderful to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Actually, I'm married now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We were also blessed with our first child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a simple life,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but a very happy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm... I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My only wish this whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,was to see you have a happy ending\Nwith a genuine smile on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}when they forced me\Nto leave you in that awful place,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}my only choice was to go home.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Miss Miyo,\Nare you happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see how I could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wasn't born with a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't even have Spirit-Sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...how can I be Lord Kudo's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How can... I be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.70,0:16:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,when I don't even belong here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo, do you have any idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...how I was able to come here\Nand see you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was pretty shocking for me\Nto get that letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure if it was real at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's awfully high-status, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kudo is a very generous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,TO HANA KANAO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}KIYOKA KUDO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He sent a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean he knows everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd always believed{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that since I didn't have\NSpirit-Sight like Kaya,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I was worthless.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have nothing to offer Lord Kudo.\NNothing of value.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's so special,\Nhow can I tell him that I'm not?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When he finds out the truth,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will he abandon me?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will he leave...\Nand take my happiness with him?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I made...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I made so many assumptions about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to know\NMr. Kudo only sent that letter for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it after knowing of the situation\Nthat you lived through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All you need now\Nis a little bit of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I know you can do it, but do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I thank you, Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I will... I'll find my courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I need... to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something\Nthat I've been holding back from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,any of the gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even possess Spirit-Sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up... working as a servant\Nfor my family in our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from a distinguished household\Nbut I don't have any skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've told you from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I intentionally withheld it out of shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you would like me to die, then I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you would prefer that I leave,\Nthen I will leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But I must thank you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for taking me into town,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for gifting me a comb...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and for everything else\Nyou've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As a sign of my gratitude,\NI made this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's small,\Nbut it's yours to do with as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I have now said everything\Nthat I would like to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Whenever you make up your mind,\NI will be here to fulfill your wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sit up and look at me, Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I ever want you to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- I have every intention
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of making our engagement official\Nas soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?\NDo you not want to live here with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I want... to stay here with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...for as long as you will allow me\Nthe privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you... to be here.\NI want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord... Lord Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, will you use this\Nto tie my hair for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lovely. I promise to cherish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you so very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing you,\Ntalking to you after all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't here\Nto share your heart with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I know that I'd still be hiding up\Nin my room right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Being near to help you is an honor for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was also just nice\Nto talk to you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Godo, drive safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kudo. I could never\Nthank you enough for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you every happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry that she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see her whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said it so many times, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How is Miyo actually doing well with Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to take some immediate action.\NShe can't fall out of our possession!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But what avenue should I take?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If she wanted it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the cards may fall into place.{\i}
